Sergey Brin

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia

This is the latest accepted revision, reviewed on 21 July 2017.




					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This name uses Eastern Slavic naming customs; the patronymic is Mikhaylovich and the family name is Brin.


Sergey Brin



Sergey Brin in 2008



Born
Sergey Mikhaylovich Brin
Серге́й Миха́йлович Брин
(1973-08-21) August 21, 1973 (age 43)
Moscow, Russian SFSR, Soviet Union[1]


Residence
Los Altos, California, U.S.


Nationality
American


Citizenship
American
Soviet (1973–79)


Alma mater
University of Maryland (B.S)
Stanford University (M.S)


Occupation
Computer scientist, Internet entrepreneur


Known for
